title: Current 1
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Rising Fortunes, Rising Spirits.

From The Peering Stones, head east towards The Peaks exit. Just before the exit, is a ramp to the south, leading to a small camp. The Current is on a ledge behind a large tent near the ramp.

title: Current 2
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Rising Fortunes, Rising Spirits.

From The Peering Stones, head south and go clockwise around the large rockface. The Current will be found on the other side, in a ruin.

title: Current 3
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Rising Fortunes, Rising Spirits.

From The Peering Stones, head northwest, through Vira Nilya, and then follow the path east to Djanan Qhat. Climb the winding path, then head to the left, and jump down the rocks to claim the Current.

title: Current 4
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Rising Fortunes, Rising Spirits.

From The Peering Stones, head northwest to the settlement of Vira Nilya. The Current is on a small cliff overlooking the settlement.

title: Current 5
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Rising Fortunes, Rising Spirits.

Head west from The Peering Stones, and climb the rocks. The Current is on a rock facing Castellum Velodyna.

title: Current 6
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Beyond the Great Wall.

Head east out of Castrum Oriens, until you come to the Velodyna River. Head south, wrapping around the cliffs, and the Current is tucked down a little nook facing the waterfall.

title: Current 7
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Beyond the Great Wall.

Head south out of Castrum Oriens, headed towards Dimwold. You'll see the Current chilling on a fallen tree.

title: Current 8
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Beyond the Great Wall.

Head east out of Castrum Oriens and cross the Velodyna River. Keep going east and you will come across a scalable mountain. Jump up and run to the far edge, where the Current lies in wait.

title: Current 9
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Beyond the Great Wall.

Head east out of Castrum Oriens until you arrive at the Velodyna River. Head north up the river, and the Current is sat on a rock.

title: Current 10
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Beyond the Great Wall.

Proceed south east out of Castrum Oriens. The Current is located under a bridge.

title: Current 1
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest In Soroban We Trust.

From Tamamizu, dive underwater, and swim west to the Isle of Zikki entrance at x10.8, y25.0, z-1.0. Swim up to The Dive, and once on land, head southwest, following the path around until you find the Current.

title: Current 2
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Once More, to the Ruby Sea.

From The Ruby Price, head north past Barrier Isle, to The Isle of Bekko. Head to the southwest corner of the island, where you'll find the Current sat on a climable rock.

title: Current 3
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Once More, to the Ruby Sea.

From The Ruby Price, head north past Barrier Isle, to The Isle of Bekko. From the southeast of the island, climb the winding cliff face and follow the edge around the island. The Current can be found overlooking the beach, opposite of where you climbed up.

title: Current 4
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Once More, to the Ruby Sea.

From Crick, head to Quickscape Pier on the north of the island. Climb aboard the boat, and head to the front. Can't miss the Current floating tauntingly in front of you.

title: Current 5
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Once More, to the Ruby Sea.

From Tamamizu, swim northeast, and loop around Shoal Rock until you arrive at The Coral Banquet. Climb to the arena at the top, run to the back and jump over the fence. The Current is hidden back here.

title: Current 6
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Once More, to the Ruby Sea.

From Crick, head northwest slightly to the Heaven-on-High structure. Begin climbing the staircases until you come to a fork. Turn left, climb the stairs, and jump onto the adjacent roof to claim your prize.

title: Current 7
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Once More, to the Ruby Sea.

From Crick, head northwest along the beach. In the middle of the island you'll find the Current, sat on a rock.

title: Current 8
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Once More, to the Ruby Sea.

From Crick, head west, and swim across to Isari. Follow the coastline north, around the large rock in the ocean and heading past the next rock until you find a hill leading up. Climb up, mind the wolves, and claim the Current.

title: Current 9
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Once More, to the Ruby Sea.

From The Ruby Price, head west, and follow the southern-most island around the Volcano. The Current is located on a small rock, on the western side of this island.

title: Current 10
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Once More, to the Ruby Sea.

Upon arriving at The Ruby Price from Kugane, jump into the water and swim straight west, until you arrive at Sakazuki. Follow the shore to the south side, and the Aether Current is a small climb up the hill.

title: Current 1
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Heavens Weep.

Enter Specula Imperatoris, and exit via the east side. Follow the path as it wraps around, headed towards The Bull's Bath. The Current is on a small cliff overlooking a body of water. Can't miss it!

title: Current 2
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Heavens Weep.

Enter Specula Imperatoris, and its just north and down a staircase from the three towers.

title: Current 3
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest The First of Many.

From Ala Ghiri, head north to Goodblade. You can't miss the Current on a wall by some barrels, overlooking the water.

title: Current 4
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest The First of Many.

From the southwestern entrance via The Fringes, follow the path around, and then head back north. The Current is up the ramp, guarded by a Kongamato.

title: Current 5
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest The First of Many.

From Ala Ghiri, head west towards The Choler. You'll see the Current on a broken bridge on your way. Simply ascend and collect!

title: Current 6
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Familiar Face Forgotten.

Head south from Ala Gannha until you reach the winding path called the Whitherwander. Head east to Momoroon's Milk, and the Current can be found by the small Qiqirn hamlet. Don't get killed!

title: Current 7
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Familiar Face Forgotten.

Enter The Peaks from Rhalgr's Reach, and head south east to The Ziggurat. Climb the first two staircases, and head right (or left!) when you can. Drop down, and head to the southern face of The Ziggurat. The Current is slightly below you, on a slight outcropping.

title: Current 8
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Familiar Face Forgotten.

From Ala Gannha, head south to Rustrock. amd then head north east, following The Thristless Path. Follow this path as it winds back on itself until you reach the Sleeping Stones. The Current is towards the back, on some bricks.

title: Current 9
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Familiar Face Forgotten.

In Ala Gannha, head north up the natural ramp and follow the path along. When you reach the railings at the end, jump over onto the small lip of the cliff where the Current waits.

title: Current 10
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Familiar Face Forgotten.

Enter The Peaks from Rhalgr's Reach, and head east. You'll see the Current a short distance away on a raise area.

title: Current 1
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Silence in Three Parts.

From Namai, travel southwest across The Glittering Basin to the Yuzuka Manor. Head northwest, following the path, to The Swallow's Compass. The Current can be found up the staircase, on the left.

title: Current 2
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Silence in Three Parts.

From Namai, travel southwest across The Glittering Basin to the Western Ryurin Bridge. The Current is hidden on the smaller, broken part of the bridge on the west bank. Just climb the short staircase to claim it.

title: Current 3
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Silence in Three Parts.

From Namai, travel southwest across The Glittering Basin to the Yuzuka Manor. A short walk north, following the path as it snakes west, and then doubling back to climb a rock face will lead you to the next Current.

title: Current 4
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Silence in Three Parts.

From Namai, travel directly south until you reach Castrum Fluminis. The Current is at the very end of the area, just past the large ring.

title: Current 5
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Silence in Three Parts.

From Namai, head directly south over the bridge, and then southeast through the archway in the wall. Carry on south down the hill and dive into the water. Swim across and carry on south westernly to find the next current - surprisingly not on top of a rock, but rather at the bottom of a small hill.

title: Current 6
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Silence in Three Parts.

From Namai, head directly south over the bridge, and then southwest to the large, broken stone arch. The Current sits in the middle, atop a steep hill.

title: Current 7
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Silence in Three Parts.

From Namai, climb the hill in the northwest of the town, and at the peak head south. Follow the cliff along to its hightest point, overlooking The Glittering Basin, and you will see the Current.

title: Current 8
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Silence in Three Parts.

From Namai, head directly south over the bridge, and then southeast through the archway in the wall. Carry on south down the hill until you see the Current sat on a peak.

title: Current 9
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Silence in Three Parts.

From Namai, climb the hill in the northwest of the town, and you'll find the Current hidden behind one of the houses.

title: Current 10
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest A Silence in Three Parts.

From Namai, head east to The Drunken Toad (near the exit to The Ruby Sea), and then south to Unseen Spirits Laughing. The Current is on a peak at the far eastern side of this area. Climb the rock to claim it.

title: Current 1
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest The Resonant.

From The Ala Mhigan Quarter, head north down the staircase and continue straight, down an alley, until you hit a fork. Turn right and head up the staircase here. Mount up, and use the flat platform on the roof to jump to the next building to the southeast. Follow this rooftop, and you'll find the Current.

title: Current 2
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Upon the Great Loch's Shore.

From Porta Praetoria, head east, and climb The White Aisle. When you see the overpass, climb either of the two towers flanking it, and circle around to climb the stairs. The Current waits at the top.

title: Current 3
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Upon the Great Loch's Shore.

From Porta Praetoria, head southeast to Sali Monastery. Enter building and exit through the hole in the wall at the back. The Current is just ahead.

title: Current 4
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Upon the Great Loch's Shore.

From Porta Praetoria, head south, following the long path starting at The Firkins, all the way to Sothwatch. The Current is hidden behind the tower here.

title: Current 5
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Upon the Great Loch's Shore.

From Porta Praetoria, head southeast towards The Saltery, and climb the staircase, Continue southeastt to the Lochwatch, a tower you can pass under, and drop to a ledge below the south side, to gain the Current.

title: Current 6
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Upon the Great Loch's Shore.

From Porta Praetoria, head east to Loch Seld. The current is on the northeasten shore, below the giant staircase.

title: Current 7
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Upon the Great Loch's Shore.

From Porta Praetoria, head northeast, around Loch Seld, and into Abalathia's Skull. Head further east, and climb the path leading to The Third Royal Casern. The Current awaits you at the end.

title: Current 8
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Upon the Great Loch's Shore.

From Porta Praetoria, go northeast, and cross the short rock bridge. Carry on along this path until you can cross another bridge southeast. Follow further along this path, climb up some rocks, and drop onto another peak, and you'll see the Current just ahead.

title: Current 9
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Upon the Great Loch's Shore.

From Porta Praetoria, head north through The High Bank, following the path around until you reach a series of rocky pathways. Ascend the ramps and double back on yourself to find a ledge you can drop to with the Current.

title: Current 10
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Upon the Great Loch's Shore.

So here we are. Aether Currents Savage. The Aether Compass' Bane (seriously, this one would not stop being triggered by my compass from anywhere).

Your first port of call is Abalathia's Skull. Head west into The Song of Kings. Keep following this path along until eventually you emerge to daylight in The Royal Hunting Grounds.

Now head south, and keep west at the fork in the road. Follow the path around until you are above the wall in High Bank, and you can drop down to claim your Current.

title: Current 5

title: Current 6
summary:

title: Current 7
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Here There Be Xaela.

From The Dawn Throne, head northwest towards Ceol Aen. The Current is sat in plain sight on a fallen pillar.

title: Current 8
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Here There Be Xaela.

From The Dawn Throne, head north, and scale the cliff near Moonrise. Follow the cliff face along to the east, and you'll find the Current hidden on a small ledge just below. Look before you leap!

title: Current 9
summary:
Becomes available during Main Story Quest Here There Be Xaela.

From Reunion, head north to The Path of the Craven. The Current is resting at the start of a broken rope bridge.

title: Current 10
